gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 116, Suns 112
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the Suns, 116-112. Cam Thomas led the way with 24 points, four assists, and two rebounds for the Nets, with Mikal Bridges adding 21 points and three rebounds in the victory. Devin Booker tallied 34 points, 12 assists, and six rebounds for the Suns in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 13-10 in the regular season, while the Suns fall to 13-11.
